article.description: — Alex Timmerman's 19 points helped Winthrop defeat Bob Jones 90-49 on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Timmerman scores 19 as Winthrop knocks off Bob Jones 90-49
article.linkText: Timmerman scores 19 as Winthrop knocks off Bob Jones 90-49
article.story: ROCK HILL, S.C. -- — Alex Timmerman's 19 points helped Winthrop defeat Bob Jones 90-49 on Tuesday night. Timmerman also had five rebounds for the Eagles (5-3). KJ Doucet scored 16 points while finishing 4 of 4 from 3-point range and 4 for 4 from the line, and added five assists. Xavier McKelvy had 11 points and was 3 of 7 shooting, including 1 for 3 from 3-point range, and went 4 for 4 from the line. Devin Pope led the way for the Bruins with 17 points. Elijah Cupples added 13 points and two blocks for Bob Jones. In addition, William Snipes finished with six points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
